OL,3,C'Shoe fetish killer' recommended for
OL,4,Cmove to open prison
OL,6,FThe Parole Board has recommended that
OL,7,Fa murderer who was dubbed the "shoe
OL,8,Ffetish killer" is moved to an open
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FChristopher Farrow, 61, was given a
OL,12,Flife sentence in November 2000, with a
OL,13,Fminimum term of 18 years, for the rape
OL,14,Fand murder of 51-year-old Wendy
OL,15,FSpeakes at her home in Wakefield.
OL,17,FFarrow was 33 when he forced his way
OL,18,Finto Ms Speakes' home in March 1994,
OL,19,Ftied her up with a pair of stockings
OL,20,Fand made her wear a pair of blue mule
OL,21,Fshoes he had brought with him.
