OL,6,FHe then raped her and stabbed her to
OL,7,Fdeath.
OL,9,FSince 2018, when he reached his
OL,10,Fminimum term, Farrow, from Cookridge
OL,11,Fin Leeds, has been denied parole three
OL,12,Ftimes, most recently in 2023.
OL,14,FHe was previously moved to an open
OL,15,Fprison in 2018 in preparation for
OL,16,Frelease, but was returned to a higher
OL,17,Fsecurity facility two years later
OL,18,Fafter a challenge.
