OL,3,C'Shoe fetish killer' recommended for
OL,4,Cmove to open prison
OL,6,FAt a hearing in February 2025, the
OL,7,FParole Board again considered whether
OL,8,Fhe could be released or moved to an
OL,9,Fopen prison.
OL,11,FIt heard that Farrow, who is now 63,
OL,12,Fhad undertaken accredited programmes
OL,13,Fin prison to address his sexual
OL,14,Foffending as well as one-on-one
OL,15,Fsessions with a psychologist.
OL,17,FThe panel heard he had "developed
OL,18,Finsight into his risk factors and had
OL,19,Fgained skills in custody linked to his
OL,20,Femotional management and problem
OL,21,Fsolving."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
