OL,3,C'Shoe fetish killer' recommended for
OL,4,Cmove to open prison
OL,6,FBut none of the witnesses who gave
OL,7,Fevidence to the panel supported him
OL,8,Fbeing freed.
OL,10,FIn its conclusion, the Parole Board
OL,11,Fsaid: "The panel noted that the index
OL,12,Foffences was a brutal, sexual, and
OL,13,Fviolent attack.
OL,15,F"Although Mr Farrow had completed
OL,16,Fextensive work in custody to explore
OL,17,Fhis offending behaviour, the panel
OL,18,Fconsidered that it was only his recent
OL,19,Fwork that had allowed professionals to
OL,20,Fsay that he had shown insight into his
OL,21,Foffending.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
