OL,3,C'Shoe fetish killer' recommended for
OL,4,Cmove to open prison
OL,6,F"Release was not supported by
OL,7,Fwitnesses and the panel was not
OL,8,Fsatisfied that release at this point
OL,9,Fwould be safe for the protection of
OL,10,Fthe public. However, on considering
OL,11,Fthe criteria for recommending
OL,12,Fplacement in open conditions, the
OL,13,Fpanel recommended that Mr Farrow
OL,14,Fshould be progressed in this way."
OL,16,FFarrow's case will be sent to the
OL,17,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood MP
OL,18,Fwho will decide whether the move to
OL,19,Fopen prison will go ahead.
